prompts.frontCover:
A minimalist 2D flat illustration of a young East Asian couple against a plain off-white background. The man (Jordan), on the right, is shown from the waist up. He has short, dark, slightly tousled hair, and a big, happy smile. He's wearing a simple tan-colored hoodie. His arms are wrapped around the woman in front of him in a gentle hug. The woman (Lao Lao), on the left, is also shown from the waist up. She has long, straight, dark hair parted to her side, and wears thin, round, gold-rimmed glasses. She's smiling contentedly with her arms crossed. She is wearing a light blue crewneck sweatshirt (no logo). The illustration style uses clean lines, simple shapes, and solid colors, capturing the couple's likeness and warm interaction from the photo.

In the center of the card, below the illustration, is text in a beautiful, readable handwritten cursive script that says: "Happy Birthday to the one who has my heart (and my hoodies)."

- Reference photos provided for character creation
- Characters should only appear on the front cover
- Transform real people into artistic cartoon/illustrated versions matching the style
- Maintain recognizable features while adapting to the artistic style
